that White had lost the control of the game. Why this happened? It is very
obvious. he played the careless move 19 Ng5. This was a move without plan. He
played Ng7, Nf7 and then he capture on e5. Actually the Knight can capture on
e5 from his initial position, f3.} 29. g3 Kb7 30. b5 {This is extremelly risky
